    h4 Add your emotional status for our survey
    form#surveyForm(name="surveyForm")
        | Select Your Gender
        br
        input#gender_m(type='radio', name='gender', value='M', checked) 
        |   
        label(for='male') Male
        |   
        input#gender_f(type='radio', name='gender', value='F', checked=gender=="Female")
        |   
